<br />
<br />But yeah, I've donloaded a lot of NSFs that reproduce the music of more recent games (sometimes using other chips like FDS or Namco), and it's quite interesting. Even if most of the people who did it did it for fun and not to actually use it in a NES game, I still find it insteresting and fun.
